Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I late too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never relaxed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dream of my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I've been fighting for it in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it never worked out. I think something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, today, you showed me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... I haven't told anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I should go to the baths now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jun? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone to the baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Bath - Men - Women
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he tell me? I'd have joined him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky, it's connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Men and women together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's in the women's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting cooked. I should get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert, having fun all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, this is the women's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Women's side? Come on, you know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's connected in the deep end. Any girls so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much steam, though. Good, good. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go to the deep end.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble. Aoi and Sanae are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard voices. Is someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get drunk and soak under the stars. Nothing beats it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll drink some more later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get cooked and get drunk. Nothing beats it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold beer will taste oh so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not just go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why let this chance go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Jun, we'll dive and peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- You'd better not.\N- Don't be so rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dizzy.\N- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You got overheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Time to get drunk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about boozers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Jun. What a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there. Then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...a she!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to tell you the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed. You saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to be embarrassed about. You're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an aspiring stage actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through many auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's worked out. But I'm determined this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the part of a girl who pretends to be a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...to get close to a boy she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to use the restaurant to practice and give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You brilliantly tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone saw through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Tomorrow is the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was my last day here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, just with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wanted to meet you as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At first I thought you were manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get close to study you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But somewhere along the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know more about men.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.78,0:25:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.72,0:25:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked Jun was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.48,0:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.65,0:25:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want her to pass this audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.95,0:25:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...and become a successful actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.29,0:25:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew about it and shared the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.43,0:25:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Koji's late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.73,0:26:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.90,0:26:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning's almost over. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.14,0:26:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't scream at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.51,0:26:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who has no business screaming at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.21,0:26:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shut up, if you don't want to get it!\N- Say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.25,0:26:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Is everybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.76,0:26:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.59,0:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you to Jun's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.90,0:26:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's joining us starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.77,0:26:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa's sister, Mina Hinomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.84,0:26:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.69,0:27:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.67,0:29:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I call you Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.57,0:29:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to, ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.48,0:29:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I thinking about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.25,0:29:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.92,0:29:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if Azusa is dating someone, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.09,0:29:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about? Aren't you having fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.96,0:29:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next episode:\NWould You Like Me to Choose Your Dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.90,0:29:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
